short_summary: Electrical repairs at the Southside Base, Newfoundland.
description: The Canadian Coast Guard HQ requires repairs to the electrical pedestal #6. This includes (1) selective replacement of conduit under the wharf portion, (2) electrical cables ran through existing conduit from the pedestal to the electrical building, and (3) new receptacles on the pedestal. The project is expected to be completed in 8 weeks.
